00:42:45,960 --> 00:42:46,227
Huh?

293
00:42:46,327 --> 00:42:47,428
How long will it last?

294
00:42:47,528 --> 00:42:48,228
My dear. How long?

295
00:42:48,520 --> 00:42:49,953
