302
00:43:15,120 --> 00:43:15,820
What's wrong with her?

303
00:43:16,400 --> 00:43:17,276
I will check her

304
00:43:17,560 --> 00:43:18,959
Take it easy. Slowly

305
00:43:21,360 --> 00:43:22,793
Relax.

306
00:43:23,920 --> 00:43:25,512
You'll be ok. Nothing to worry about

307
00:43:28,440 --> 00:43:29,395
Umbilical cord...

308
00:43:30,280 --> 00:43:31,190
You are away

309
00:43:32,840 --> 00:43:33,795
