310
00:43:34,240 --> 00:43:34,940
Don't see, don't see

311
00:43:37,520 --> 00:43:39,590
Breath deeply. Breath deeply

312
00:43:40,200 --> 00:43:41,918
We'll go to the operating room

313
00:43:42,680 --> 00:43:44,716
...you are so panicked

314
