you will hurt the baby

315
00:43:46,520 --> 00:43:47,396
We'll arrive soon

316
00:43:47,600 --> 00:43:49,079
Talk to her...distract her attention

317
00:43:51,040 --> 00:43:53,679
Darling. Relax. Don't worry

318
00:43:54,640 --> 00:43:55,595
I will be with you forever

319
00:43:55,960 --> 00:43:57,313
Don't push too hard! 
You will hurt the baby

320
00:43:57,800 --> 00:43:59,995
Baby's head is out. Careful!

321
00:44:04,160 --> 00:44:04,700
Darling

322
00:44:04,800 --> 00:44:06,756
Mrs. Listen to me

323
00:44:07,320 --> 00:44:09,268
the child will be born soon

324
00:44:09,368 --> 00:44:11,590
We'll help you here, ok?

325
00:44:11,720 --> 00:44:12,420
You must try your best

326
00:44:12,720 --> 00:44:14,153
and the child will too

327
00:44:15,720 --> 00:44:17,358
Ok, let's begin

328
00:44:20,640 --> 00:44:23,029
Push...Push.

329
00:44:23,560 --> 00:44:25,039
Push.

330
00:44:59,360 --> 00:45:00,270
Did you see?

331
00:45:00,400 --> 00:45:01,230
Don't bother her

332
00:45:01,680 --> 00:45:02,380
Don't look. Don't

333
00:45:02,960 --> 00:45:03,660
Push. You will be ok

334
00:45:18,320 --> 00:45:19,639
Come on. Baby will be born soon

335
00:45:19,840 --> 00:45:21,796
Quickly...the baby is so close now

336
00:45:22,760 --> 00:45:23,510
Try. Try your best!

337
00:45:38,880 --> 00:45:40,313
Don't shout!

338
00:46:08,400 --> 00:46:09,310
Is the child ok?

339
00:46:09,560 --> 00:46:10,879
Call Emergency

340
00:46:13,800 --> 00:46:15,313
Prepare to save its life

341
00:46:47,520 --> 00:46:48,999
Don't hurt my baby!

342
00:46:52,320 --> 00:46:54,276
Don't hurt!

343
00:47:04,320 --> 00:47:05,827
Come on, help me! 
There is another patient inside

344
00:47:05,927 --> 00:47:06,875
Hurry!

345
00:47:09,000 --> 00:47:09,848
Don't move

346
00:47:09,948 --> 00:47:15,313
Slowly...slowly..

347
00:47:52,920 --> 00:47:53,909
Buddha said

348
00:47:54,320 --> 00:48:00,847
Everything will be ok

349
00:48:00,947 --> 00:48:03,849
but sometimes humans are very stupid

350
00:48:03,949 --> 00:48:06,912
we are far away from the wisdom

351
00:48:07,880 --> 00:48:08,790
away and away

352
00:48:11,040 --> 00:48:16,910
if we run into problems

353
