and we still think 
we can control everything

355
00:48:32,960 --> 00:48:35,952
These people spend 
2 hours taking the bus everyday

356
00:48:36,320 --> 00:48:37,753
in order to come here to study the exercise

357
00:48:39,840 --> 00:48:41,114
They are all terminal cancer patients

358
00:48:42,280 --> 00:48:45,317
Life and death is only a way of life

359
00:48:50,480 --> 00:48:51,435
No matter what happens

360
00:48:52,000 --> 00:48:53,479
we should still be alive in this world

361
00:48:54,920 --> 00:48:56,478
We always ask ourselves

362
00:48:57,200 --> 00:48:58,315
Why is my own life the worst in the world?

363
00:48:59,040 --> 00:49:01,952
In fact, life is in our hearts

364
00:49:03,040 --> 00:49:06,794
When we meet some troubles

365
00:49:07,240 --> 00:49:07,940
We will have different reasons to avoid them

366
00:49:07,986 --> 00:49:11,396
Explain what is fate, what is bad

367
00:49:12,400 --> 00:49:14,277
Because our hearts are full of sadness

368
00:49:14,800 --> 00:49:16,279
If we can find out what causes our sadness

369
00:49:17,120 --> 00:49:18,678
Everthing will be solved

370
00:50:00,440 --> 00:50:02,510
Take me to Tongluowan, Huanshibao

371
00:52:10,240 --> 00:52:11,912
Miss, is everything ok?

372
00:52:24,920 --> 00:52:26,399
What's the matter?

373
00:53:36,320 --> 00:53:39,118
Sister, did you see my dad?

374
00:53:39,360 --> 00:53:42,477
It's too late, why isn't your dad back?

375
00:53:42,960 --> 00:53:45,838
Sister, did you see my dad?

376
00:54:28,040 --> 00:54:29,439
Ok. Ok. Well done!

377
00:54:29,560 --> 00:54:30,436
Raise your left leg

378
00:54:36,160 --> 00:54:38,151
Come on.

379
00:54:39,400 --> 00:54:41,038
Great. Come on.

380
00:54:45,440 --> 00:54:48,034
Ok. Relax. 
Do your best to raise your leg

381
00:54:57,440 --> 00:54:59,431
Good! Well done!!

382
00:55:00,520 --> 00:55:02,636
It is very important to do this exercise

383
00:55:03,040 --> 00:55:05,713
before you give birth

384
00:55:05,920 --> 00:55:08,912
use the water. You will feel better

385
00:55:09,840 --> 00:55:10,795
Ok. Go on.

386
00:55:11,040 --> 00:55:12,109
Well done!

387
00:55:51,240 --> 00:55:53,674
I will enter the hospital next week

388
00:55:55,600 --> 00:55:56,510
Why?

389
00:55:57,720 --> 00:55:59,836
You don't need to be there
until your baby's birth

390
00:56:00,720 --> 00:56:03,234
I always have bad dreams at night now

391
00:56:05,720 --> 00:56:06,709
Dreams my baby was born

392
00:56:07,000 --> 00:56:09,070
but without arms and legs

393
00:56:10,000 --> 00:56:11,718
My doctor suggested I stay in the hospital

394
00:56:11,880 --> 00:56:13,871
It is better than staying at home alone

395
00:56:14,840 --> 00:56:18,719
My husband is not at home, so I think
it's better to stay in the hospital

396
00:56:18,880 --> 00:56:22,873
Otherwise my daughter will be scared
when I give birth suddenly

397
00:56:58,240 --> 00:56:59,719
What are you doing?

398
00:57:04,880 --> 00:57:06,871
Why are you there?

399
00:57:08,840 --> 00:57:10,717
Jiawen, what's wrong with you?

400
00:57:11,520 --> 00:57:12,589
What's going on?

401
00:57:14,920 --> 00:57:17,115
Get out! Get out!

402
00:57:33,000 --> 00:57:35,389
Jiawen, what's wrong with you?

403
00:58:09,200 --> 00:58:10,633
She was beating others in a restaurant

404
00:58:11,120 --> 00:58:13,395
She already took tranquilizers

405
00:58:13,920 --> 00:58:15,558
According to her regular doctor,

406
00:58:15,720 --> 00:58:16,869
she is a little depressed

407
00:58:22,120 --> 00:58:23,030
What's wrong? Jiawen

408
00:58:25,320 --> 00:58:26,020
Doctor!

409
00:58:27,040 --> 00:58:28,632
He wants to hurt Mrs. Zhou's baby

410
00:58:31,440 --> 00:58:32,998
Tell Mrs. Zhou

411
00:58:34,880 --> 00:58:37,269
he wants to get her

412
00:58:39,520 --> 00:58:40,748
There is somebody 
who can look after Mrs. Zhou

413
00:58:42,400 --> 00:58:44,391
Can we take care of your baby?

414
00:59:04,720 --> 00:59:06,312
I can help you

415
00:59:06,520 --> 00:59:08,476
to see your baby

416
00:59:09,360 --> 00:59:10,060
Ok.

417
00:59:16,560 --> 00:59:17,834
Enn...it is a bit painful

418
00:59:32,560 --> 00:59:33,788
Just relax

419
00:59:34,880 --> 00:59:35,790
Don't move

420
00:59:36,160 --> 00:59:38,116
You see, everything is ok

421
00:59:43,920 --> 00:59:45,672
Baby's feet are moving!

422
00:59:46,240 --> 00:59:47,309
Can you see?

423
00:59:51,880 --> 00:59:52,869
Isn't that funny?

424
00:59:55,920 --> 00:59:58,354
Baby is very healthy. Don't worry

425
01:00:21,800 --> 01:00:26,715
That woman in the train station
really wanted to hurt my baby!

426
01:00:27,760 --> 01:00:29,557
Every happening has its own reason

427
01:00:30,320 --> 01:00:31,305
If you never did 
anything bad to other people

428
01:00:34,000 --> 01:00:35,877
you shouldn't care 
about something so strange

429
01:00:39,000 --> 01:00:40,718
Why must I accept this bad experience?

430
01:00:42,320 --> 01:00:43,912
I have never hurt others

431
01:00:45,160 --> 01:00:45,910
Why am I being treated like this?

432
01:00:46,080 --> 01:00:48,116
Everything can be solved by a pure heart

433
01:00:48,440 --> 01:00:50,908
I think you're always avoiding something

434
01:00:52,040 --> 01:00:54,031
Only you know what you avoid

435
01:00:57,720 --> 01:01:02,157
Who is she? Who on earth is she??

436
01:01:28,000 --> 01:01:29,319
Get out!!

437
01:01:33,880 --> 01:01:35,313
Get out!!

438
01:01:46,400 --> 01:01:47,310
Get out!!

439
01:01:54,520 --> 01:01:58,069
There was a woman who killed herself
here before, wasn't there?

440
01:01:59,320 --> 01:02:01,788
Miss, I've only been working here
for a few days, I don't know

441
01:02:02,600 --> 01:02:05,114
I can't answer any questions

442
01:02:06,000 --> 01:02:06,910
I'm sorry

443
01:02:08,240 --> 01:02:09,116
Next!

444
01:02:14,920 --> 01:02:16,399
Hello. Xiao Dai?

445
01:02:17,320 --> 01:02:20,710
Please find some information about that woman
who wanted to kill herself on the train

446
01:02:21,520 --> 01:02:22,589
I'm writing about her

447
01:02:23,440 --> 01:02:25,715
I also need her picture and address

448
01:02:26,400 --> 01:02:28,311
I want to visit her family

449
01:02:33,360 --> 01:02:34,873
I looked for files all last night

450
01:02:35,640 --> 01:02:36,629
But only found two cases

451
01:03:22,520 --> 01:03:24,397
Can I vist Miss Zhang?

452
01:03:25,720 --> 01:03:26,709
Who's there?

453
01:03:27,880 --> 01:03:28,915
Sir... someone wants to visit

454
01:03:49,000 --> 01:03:50,399
Why did you lie to me?

455
01:03:52,320 --> 01:03:53,878
It's already over

456
01:03:56,320 --> 01:03:57,878
Don't think about it anymore, ok?

457
01:04:02,760 --> 01:04:05,718
Don't lie to yourself! We killed her!

458
01:04:07,960 --> 01:04:10,394
Why didn't you tell me?
your wife killed herself?

459
01:04:13,520 --> 01:04:15,511
We had already broken up!

460
01:04:16,520 --> 01:04:18,556
Why did your wife kill herself?

461
01:04:21,640 --> 01:04:22,709
Don't you know?

462
01:04:23,440 --> 01:04:25,874
Now...she wants to make me die..

463
01:04:28,720 --> 01:04:31,712
Tell her...Tell her!

464
01:04:32,720 --> 01:04:35,314
I didn't make you leave your wife

465
01:04:37,320 --> 01:04:38,719
Yes..It was me..I killed her!

466
01:04:39,440 --> 01:04:41,158
That night

467
01:04:42,440 --> 01:04:43,429
you called me

468
01:04:43,880 --> 01:04:44,915
I miss you!

469
01:04:47,160 --> 01:04:49,230
Me too...where are you now?

470
01:04:51,000 --> 01:04:52,513
Did you tell her about us?

471
01:04:53,320 --> 01:04:54,912
I can't tell you now. 
She's here

472
01:04:55,800 --> 01:04:57,153
I can't wait for you for such a long time!

473
01:04:58,560 --> 01:04:59,260
Don't be mad

474
01:04:59,720 --> 01:05:02,837
No...I want you to be with me right now!

475
01:05:03,840 --> 01:05:04,909
Call me in a bit

476
01:05:18,080 --> 01:05:20,548
It's her call! Don't answer!

477
01:05:21,320 --> 01:05:23,788
Please...don't answer!

478
01:05:24,880 --> 01:05:26,871
We can pretend nothing 
happened between you two

479
01:05:27,320 --> 01:05:28,719
I didn't hear anything

480
01:05:31,280 --> 01:05:32,713
Don't answer

481
01:05:33,480 --> 01:05:35,835
We can pretend nothing 
happened between you two

482
01:05:52,440 --> 01:05:54,317
Why do you treat me like this?

483
01:05:57,120 --> 01:05:58,394
You will regret it

484
01:05:59,520 --> 01:06:02,114
I will make you regret it forever!

485
01:06:08,240 --> 01:06:08,940
Hello?

486
01:06:10,240 --> 01:06:11,832
Are you ok?

487
01:06:12,000 --> 01:06:14,434
I will call you

488
01:06:15,160 --> 01:06:17,355
You asked me to call you in a bit

489
01:06:18,640 --> 01:06:20,119
I will make you regret it forever!

490
01:06:32,040 --> 01:06:32,756
Hello.

491
01:06:32,880 --> 01:06:33,580
Hello.

492
01:06:54,520 --> 01:06:55,919
What's happened?

493
01:06:58,440 --> 01:07:00,431
It's me that killed her

494
01:07:00,920 --> 01:07:02,433
I'm sorry

495
01:07:04,400 --> 01:07:05,100
Why did eveything go so wrong?

496
01:07:16,760 --> 01:07:18,751
I'm leaving. Xiao Zhang

497
01:07:19,520 --> 01:07:20,475
Get some rest, ok?

498
01:07:37,480 --> 01:07:39,471
Can we talk now?

499
01:07:42,400 --> 01:07:44,152
I think...

500
01:07:45,440 --> 01:07:46,919
We should break up

501
01:07:50,040 --> 01:07:53,953
It's not good when we're together

502
01:07:58,640 --> 01:07:59,629
I feel so bad

503
01:08:01,120 --> 01:08:02,553
And I think your wife's feeling it too

504
01:08:08,920 --> 01:08:10,911
Let's part from now on

505
01:08:16,320 --> 01:08:17,753
Go back to your wife

506
01:08:18,000 --> 01:08:19,228
What the hell are you saying?

507
01:08:19,440 --> 01:08:20,388
What do you mean?

508
01:08:20,488 --> 01:08:21,029
We have already killed her!

509
01:08:21,129 --> 01:08:23,156
Your wife is waiting for you to have dinner

510
01:08:35,120 --> 01:08:36,917
I'm leaving

511
01:08:39,640 --> 01:08:41,232
It's too late

512
01:08:43,120 --> 01:08:44,633
We have already killed her

513
01:08:45,200 --> 01:08:45,900
No

514
01:08:46,480 --> 01:08:48,516
Not me!

515
01:08:49,520 --> 01:08:51,317
I didn't kill her!

516
01:08:51,640 --> 01:08:53,631
It's she who wanted to kill my baby!

517
01:08:58,800 --> 01:09:00,313
What's wrong with you?

518
01:09:10,440 --> 01:09:11,395
Mrs. Zhou

519
01:09:15,640 --> 01:09:16,914
I don't want to give birth to this baby

520
01:09:19,520 --> 01:09:21,397
She made me have such a bad experience

521
01:09:52,040 --> 01:09:54,395
Some people in this world never
want to face the pain

522
01:09:56,720 --> 01:09:58,517
They choose to avoid being hurt

523
01:09:59,240 --> 01:10:01,879
force themselves to forget everything

524
01:10:02,120 --> 01:10:03,792
even pretend nothing happened

525
01:10:05,400 --> 01:10:06,992
they will do their best

526
01:10:07,720 --> 01:10:10,439
to stop something from happening

527
01:10:11,880 --> 01:10:13,757
Jiawen is one of them

528
01:10:14,080 --> 01:10:17,038
