when your wife was still alive

529
01:10:17,160 --> 01:10:19,913
And asked you about your relationship
in that virtual space

530
01:10:20,520 --> 01:10:22,556
She thought if your relationship was over
before your wife died, it would be better

531
01:10:24,720 --> 01:10:27,553
But...she still can't forget that you
hurt your wife and let her die

532
01:10:30,160 --> 01:10:31,991
She has some psychological problems

533
01:10:33,840 --> 01:10:37,389
She couldn't stop the illusion
even though she was hurt by you

534
01:10:37,920 --> 01:10:40,150
In a word

535
01:10:40,400 --> 01:10:43,312
She is searching for a special way
to save your wife

536
01:10:49,880 --> 01:10:53,634
Please help her

537
01:10:55,920 --> 01:10:57,717
I have already made my wife die

538
01:10:59,320 --> 01:11:00,719
so I don't want to make her die too

539
01:11:01,640 --> 01:11:03,710
and our baby

540
01:11:05,040 --> 01:11:07,315
We must wait for the birth of the baby

541
01:11:07,760 --> 01:11:10,752
It's too dangerous to take medicine now

542
01:12:06,160 --> 01:12:09,311
Don't let him hurt your baby! Mrs. Zhou

543
01:12:09,920 --> 01:12:12,639
Don't hurt her baby! Mrs. Zhou

544
01:12:19,760 --> 01:12:20,749
I can't stand the pain!

545
01:12:22,320 --> 01:12:23,309
Mrs. Zhou

546
01:12:26,760 --> 01:12:28,239
The baby is coming out, here

547
01:12:28,640 --> 01:12:29,755
Your baby will be out soon

548
01:12:29,880 --> 01:12:30,756
Relax. Take it easy

549
01:12:38,120 --> 01:12:39,314
Push...

550
01:12:41,440 --> 01:12:42,759
Breathe, breathe

551
01:12:48,920 --> 01:12:50,273
Again. Again

552
01:13:08,480 --> 01:13:09,469
Baby is out

553
01:13:23,680 --> 01:13:24,669
Here's your baby

554
01:13:42,160 --> 01:13:43,513
He is not her baby!

555
01:15:16,160 --> 01:15:17,832
Baby, everything is ok

556
01:16:09,720 --> 01:16:11,153
Her baby is about to be born!

557
01:16:11,320 --> 01:16:12,639
carry her to the operating room
as quickly as possible

558
01:16:27,880 --> 01:16:30,440
Baby's dad is an artist

559
01:16:31,920 --> 01:16:32,620
After we broke up

560
01:16:34,160 --> 01:16:36,151
